title: Winning numbers drawn in 'MassCash' game
maintext:
BRAINTREE, Mass. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Massachusetts Lottery’s “MassCash” game were:
21-23-28-30-31
(twenty-one, twenty-three, twenty-eight, thirty, thirty-one)
